{"tid":730664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國促放劉霞　外交部：中國政府比任何國家更關心中國公民健康","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T23:30:22.000Z","uid":53379,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ca48a0ee0d2c2490f92032df8270472c71aa4b78","tid":730664,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聯合國促放劉霞　外交部：中國政府比任何國家更關心中國公民健康</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180705/s00004/2518bbc4cc1eeafd113f940a8b80d97a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180705%2Fs00004%2F2518bbc4cc1eeafd113f940a8b80d97a.jpg&h=3de43a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波遺孀劉霞狀况令人堪憂，聯合國一批人權專家周三（4日）發出聯合聲明，表示擔憂劉霞的健康，要求中國立即公開劉霞身在何處及將她釋放。中國外交部發言人陸慷今日重申，劉霞是中國公民，「中國政府會依法保護中國公民的合法權益」，又稱中國政府「比任何其他國家的人」，更關心中國公民的健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部亞太區部長田銘祺（Mark Field）上周亦表示，英方非常關注劉霞狀況，要求中國政府尊重其出國意願，撤消所有對她的限制。陸慷當時質疑，英國政府「有何資格」提出有關要求。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180705/s00004/1530788750361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180705%2Fs00004%2F1530788750361&d=wfwEOzrquiZZpp7W%2FLLl%2FjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=cc31526e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180705%2Fs00004%2F1530788750361&h=b9c6c26e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180705/s00004/1530788750361</a>"},{"pid":"2fb78b33d3164068206965ecaae3f8c7c4cf33e9","tid":730664,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"口交部：中國政府<span style=\"color: red;\">比任何國家更關心</span>中國公民健康<br />\n人唔笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i